====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# One who [[clap]]s.
# An object so suspended inside a [[bell]] that it may hit the bell and cause it to ring.
# A wooden mechanical device used as a [[scarecrow]]; bird-scaring [[rattle]], a wind-rattle or a wind-clapper.

